title: 147: College Football Playoff preview
itunes:title: 147: College Football Playoff preview
description:
Special guest Matt "Money" Smith joins Bucky Brooks to preview the College Football Playoff. The duo discusses how Clemson's Deshaun Watson and Mike Williams matchup against Urban Meyer and Greg Schiano's Ohio State defense. Money and Bucky also preview Washington vs. Alabama.
